INSERT INTO `gdt_solutions_detail` VALUES (1,'Mobile App','#','Module-app-banner1.jpg','','App1.jpg','Greystone Data Technology develops new and innovative on-device applications for the Mobile Device Lifecycle.','[{\"name\":\"app.png\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',1,1,1,'',0,2,0,'#FFFFFF',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-24 15:19:28','1','2016-08-03 11:24:49',0),(2,'SELF-E App','#','SELFE1a.jpg','','SELFE1a.jpg','The SELF-E&trade; application utilizes one of our Patented technologies to evaluate the cosmetic condition of a mobile device&#39;s front glass, display panel, and back cover. This cutting edge technology does not require any additional hardware aside from the use of a mirror to take the SELF-E&trade;. It analyzes the display condition utilizing the smartphone&#39;s CPU, and front &amp; back cameras. This powerful tool allows anyone to quickly and confidently verify the cosmetic condition of their device&rsquo;s display panel, front glass, and back cover anywhere with only their mobile device and a mirror.','[{\"name\":\"app_layer_b.png\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',1,3,1,'',0,1,1,'#606060',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-24 15:20:38','1','2018-06-29 10:23:15',0),(3,'EcoFunc App','#','EcoFunc1a.jpg','','smartmockups.png','The EcoFunc application is a powerful tool that utilizes the technologies from both our patent pending SELF-E&trade; and Efunc solutions. This on-device solution is capable of running a complete battery of extensive functional tests, and accurately evaluating the cosmetic condition of the mobile device&rsquo;s front screen. The combination of these solutions allows Greystone to offer an on-device product capable of providing the most accurate and complete test results. This application eliminates the needs for expensive testing hardware, and allows even the most average smartphone user to perform such a robust and conclusive test of their device.','[{\"name\":\"app_layer_c.png\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',1,6,1,