s GCS to expand and contract as customer demand requires. This gives assurance to every customer that any fluctuation in processing can be met with equal cloud services support for Greystone solutions.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nAll transactions are safely and securely stored in GCS databases for later access for reporting, production analysis, and certifying processes such as device erasure. Easy and secure access to the stored data through the GCS dashboard gives customers easy access to reports and real time data through an attractive web interface.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nIn addition to traditional web based Internet access, Greystone will soon be providing apps on Android and Apple devices enabling more immediate information access right on the production floor.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nAll Greystone technology is designed to function together using the Greystone Cloud Services as a communication conduit, a stored data location, and a synchronization engine. Greystone technology functions seamlessly and smoothly providing end to end solutions from the consumer experience to retail environment to the warehouse.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nBehind the scenes the GCS helps all the technology work reliably, smoothly, and flawlessly 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, every week of the year.</p>','[{\"name\":\"cloud1.jpg\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',1,2,2,'',0,1,0,'#606060',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 12:57:35','1','2016-08-02 04:52:07',0),(7,'Core Technology ( Icombine, Izap, Reta, Itest, Etc,..)','#','cloud2.jpg','','cloud_img2_mobile.jpg','This is Photoshop&#39;s version of Lorem Ipsum. Proin gravida nibh vel velit auctor aliquet. Aenean sollicitudin, lorem quis bibendum auctor, nisi elit consequat ipsum, nec sagittis sem nibh id elit. Duis sed odio sit amet nibh vulputate cursus a sit amet mauris. Morbi accumsan ipsum velit.','[{\"name\":\"cloud2.jpg\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',0,3,2,NULL,0,2,0,'#606060',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 12:58:29','1','2016-06-04 15: