 cutting edge technology. The device functionality can be measured to determine the value of the device before it is traded in or sold. Plus, the associate may simply transfer the customer data from the old device to their new device. Small and featured packed, this system will make any point of sale associate an expert with mobile device buying.','[{\"name\":\"IMG_9794 copy.png\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}%5',1,4,3,'',0,1,1,'#606060',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 13:20:10','1','2016-08-17 09:21:24',0),(11,'Izap Software','#','IzapIpad copy.png','','IzapIpad copy.png','The Izap Software technology is a complete mobile device evaluation solution, designed to enhance the customer experience in the retail environment. The key functionalities of this software are for trade-in assistance, claim adjudication/validation, extensive diagnostic tests, quickly transfer content between same or different device operating systems, secure data erasure with solution has been certified by ADISA, and provisioning on the mobile device. Supports over 1000 smartphone devices from all major manufactures.','[{\"name\":\"Izap-SW-2_Mobile.jpg\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',1,5,3,'',0,2,1,'#606060',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 13:20:59','1','2019-03-15 15:29:22',0),(12,'Itest Chamber ','#','iTest_RightView_Opened-and-Closed-with-Android-phone_PC.png','','iTest_RightView_Opened-and-Closed-with-Android-phone_Mobile.png','The Itest Chamber is a hardware technology developed to eliminate the needfor manual functional tests on the mobile device. The Itest Chamber is a sturdy, compact unit that is capable of running extensive and automatic tests such as: camera, video record, LED / flash, proximity sensor, Wi-Fi, call and all audio functions. The capability of automatically testing these features on the mobile device will improve the experience for both the customer and the retail clerk by reducing the time to manually inspect the device for any flaws. Supports over 1000 smartphone devices from manufactures such as: Apple, Nokia, Samsung, LG, BlackBerry, Casio, HTC, Motorola, Pantech, Sanyo, Sharp, Sony Ericsson, and more.','[{\"name\":\"IMG_9863 copy.png\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',0,0,3,'',0,1,1,'#606060',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 13:22:19','1','2016-08-17 11:21:58',0),(13,'Repair Center','#','Repair-banner.jpg','Repair&nbsp;','repair_banner_mobile.jpg','Greystone Data Technology develops innovative and robust repair equipment to precisely evaluate the functionality and cosmetics of a mobile device.','[{\"name\":\"Repair-banner.jpg\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',1,1,5,'',0,2,1,'#000000',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 13:27:45','1','2016-09-05 10:57:07',0),(14,'Izap Software','#','IzapIpad copy.png','','IzapIpad copy.png','&nbsp; The Izap Software technology is a complete mobile device evaluation solution&nbsp; designed to enhance the customer experience in the retail environment. The key&nbsp; functionalities of this software are for trade-in assistance, claim&nbsp; adjudication/validation, extensive diagnostic tests, quickly transfer content between&nbsp; same or different operating systems (OS), secure data erasure with solution has been certified by ADISA, and provisioning on the&nbsp; mobile device. Supports over 1000 smartphone devices from manufactures such as:&nbsp; Apple, Nokia, Samsung, LG, BlackBerry, Casio, HTC, Motorola, Pantech, Sanyo, Sharp,&nbsp; Sony Ericsson, and more.','[{\"name\":\"Repair1.jpg\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',0,4,5,'',0,1,1,'#606060',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 13:28:48','1','2019-03-15 15:30:38',0),(15,'Itest Chamber','#','iTest_RightView_Opened-and-Closed-with-Android-phone_PC.png','','iTest_RightView_Opened-and-Closed-with-Android-phone_Mobile.png','<p>The Itest Chamber is a hardware technology developed to eliminate the need for manual functional tests on the mobile device. The Itest Chamber is a sturdy, compact unit that is capable of running extensive and automatic tests such as: Wi-Fi, Audio, proximity sensor, call signal functionality, and more. The capability of automatically testing these features on the mobile device will eliminate human error, and increase throughput of devices completed by the operator. After each device is processed it will give the operator a gauge on the functional status of the device.</p>\n\n<p>Supports over 1000 smartphone devices from manufactures such as: Apple, Nokia, Samsung, LG, BlackBerry, Casio, HTC, Motorola, Pantech, Sanyo, Sharp, Sony Ericsson, and more.</p>','[{\"name\":\"IMG_9863 copy.png\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',1,6,5,'',0,1,1,'#606060',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 13:29:41','1','2016-08-17 11:28:45',0),(16,'Efunc App','#','Repair3_PC.jpg','','Repair(3)_Phone.jpg','<div>Efunc is an application developed to perform a functional diagnostic test for the mobile device. The tests involves mostly automatic tests to reduce human error and maximize user experience.<br />\nThis application is useful for operators in the repair facility to be given the ability to run this application and test the functionality of the device. This reduces the time and cost for the operator going through a manual process of checking each feature of the mobile device.</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-left: 1in;\">&nbsp;</div>','[{\"name\":\"chart.png\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',0,0,5,NULL,0,1,0,'#606060',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 13:30:39','1','2016-07-20 03:29:02',0),(17,'Processing Center','#','Processing_PC.jpg','','Processing-Mobile.jpg','Greystone Data Technology designs a diverse catalogue of powerful equipment that promotes productivity and revenue, while reducing human error.','[{\"name\":\"warehouse-banner.jpg\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',1,1,6,'',0,2,1,'#ffffff',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 13:34:38','1','2016-08-17 13:35:13',0),(18,'All-In-One (AIO)','#','iCombine-FlatTray-LeftView-With-Android-and-iPhone_on-PC.png','','iCombine-FlatTray-LeftView-With-Android-and-iPhone-_-on-Mobile.png','The AIO is an advanced all-inclusive mobile testing platform designed for use in warehouse or production environments. This system is very versatile and scalable for any size of operation. The AIO is able to receive mobile devices into your Warehouse Management System (WMS), test the full functionality of a mobile device, remove and sanitize all data from the mobile device with data erasure solution has been certified by ADISA. One machine does it all. All information about the device, tests, and content sanitization is maintained in an off-site database the customer may access at any time. This gives you end to end reporting of devices at the IMEI level.&nbsp;One computer can support up to 4 Icombine (hardware)&nbsp;modules. Each Icombine module can support up to 8 mobile devices at one time.&nbsp;Our system is the <strong><em>only</em></strong> system that can process your Android, Apple, BlackBerry and Windows devices all at the same time on the same Icombine module. No need for dedicated equipment or redundant computer systems.&nbsp;Supports over 1000 smartphone devices from every major manufacture.','[{\"name\":\"iCombine-FlatTray-LeftView-With-Android-and-iPhone_on-PC.png\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1},{\"name\":\"iCombine-Vertical-tray-_LeftView-with-Android-and-iPhone_PC.png\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',1,2,6,'',0,2,1,'#606060',2,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 13:36:19','1','2019-03-15 17:31:03',0),(19,'Receiving Imaging Technology','#','RIT-RightView-With-Devices-02_on-PC.png','','RIT-RightView-With-Devices-02_on-Mobile.png','<p>Relying on powerful OCR algorithms to convert captured images to machine text and data. The RIT machine receives device information without requiring connection to a computer or the device to power on. This innovative system is capable of reading the Human readable information on the back of a mobile device, then parsing the information out to a computer in machine language. You no longer need to read an IMEI on the back of a device and type it into a computer. The data is analyzed and presented in industry accepted formats. The RIT system also reads bar codes in any orientation adding to the versatility of this system. You may even connect a mobile device to the KIT system to read the internal information. The KIT has barcode scanner emulation with programmable keystroke output via USB connection. The KIT provides complete productivity reporting, which is available on our cloud based Dashboard.</p>','[{\"name\":\"IMG_9868 copy.png\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":0}]',1,3,6,'',0,1,1,'#606060',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 13:37:25','1','2016-08-17 13:34:22',0),(20,'Kitting Imaging Technology','#','KIT_LeftView_New_PC.png','','KIT_LeftView_New_Mobile.png','<p>KIT is a Quality Control (QC) system utilizing machine vision to reduce the number of errors encountered from products not placed into boxes. The use of a real time camera to detect if an item is in the box allows for &ldquo;on-the-fly&rdquo; QC of the box contents as it is carried along on a conveyor belt. This system is capable of tracking the quantity of product by Stock Keeping Unit (SKU) consumed as the build is progressing. Optimization of the order fulfillment process is achieved by checking the contents of the package before the lid is sealed. Versatility of the systems allows it to be used on moving conveyor lines or in a stand-alone packing station.&nbsp; You may generate various production reports by retrieving data that is collected in our easy to use Dashboard. The system is fully integrated, small, convenient, easy to use and accurate.</p>','[{\"name\":\"KIT_LeftView_New_PC.png\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',1,4,6,'',0,2,1,'#606060',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 13:39:07','1','2016-08-17 13:33:59',0),(21,'Call Center','#','Call-center-banner.jpg','','callcenter_banner_mobile.jpg','Greystone Data Technology provides a dynamic and intuitive Call Center solution that assists the Call Center associate to quickly diagnose and resolve common issues through automated remote testing.','[{\"name\":\"Call-center-banner.jpg\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',1,1,4,NULL,0,1,0,'#606060',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 15:05:07','1','2016-07-15 08:16:00',0),(22,'Efunc App','#','Call-Center(2)_PC.jpg','','Call Center(2) Mobile.jpg','Efunc is an application developed to perform a functional diagnostic test for the mobile device. The assessments involve mostly automatic tests to reduce human error and maximize user experience. This application is useful in a Call Center environment for both the call center operator and the customer. After the mobile device has been processed, the results will allow the call center operator to distinguish the specific issue the customer is experiencing. This cuts down costs, and time spent resolving the issue.','[{\"name\":\"call-center1.jpg\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',0,2,4,NULL,0,1,0,'#606060',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 15:06:33','1','2016-07-20 03:28:51',0),(23,'Core Technology (CT: Icombine, Izap, Reta, Itest, Etc..)','#','call-center2.jpg','','callcenter_img2_mobile.jpg','This is Photoshop&#39;s version of Lorem Ipsum. Proin gravida nibh vel velit auctor aliquet. Aenean sollicitudin, lorem quis bibendum auctor, nisi elit consequat ipsum, nec sagittis sem nibh id elit. Duis sed odio sit amet nibh vulputate cursus a sit amet mauris. Morbi accumsan ipsum velit.','[{\"name\":\"call-center2.jpg\",\"label\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"display\":1}]',1,3,4,NULL,0,2,0,'#606060',0,0,0,'1','2016-05-26 15:07:19','1','2016-06-04 11:02:32',1),(24,'Technology Scenario (Call center)','#','chart.png','','chart_mobile.png','This is Photoshop&#39;s version of Lorem Ipsum. Proin gravida nibh vel velit auctor aliquet. Aenean sollicitudin, lorem quis bibendum auctor, nisi elit consequat ipsum, nec sagittis sem nibh id elit. Duis sed odio sit amet nibh vulputate cursus a sit amet mauris. Morbi accumsan ipsum velit. 